==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪʃǝn|-eɪʃǝn]]

===Noun===

'''classification'''

#The act of forming into a [[class]] or classes; a distribution into [[group]]s, as classes, orders, families, etc., according to some common [[relation]]s or affinities.

